Cell["\<\
As the Hilbert space associated with fermions is finite dimensional, one can \
find an operator expression for fermions from a matrix representation in a \
systematic way.\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->755181075,ExpressionUUID->"038c5095-6664-419d-8a9f-dfbb56ac696d"],

