representation mat and acting on the system consisting of the species {s1, \
s2, ...}. ExpressionFor[vec, {s1, s2, ...}] returns the state vector \
corresponding to the column vector representation vec and acting on the \
system consisting of the species {s1, s2, ...}. ExpressionFor[mat, s] is \
equivalent to ExpressionFor[mat, {s}]. ExpressionFor[vec, s] is equivalent to \
